		font-weight: 500;
		color: var(--primary);
		margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
	}

	h3 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		color: #333;
		margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
	}

